name: E L V N T H

metadata.name: God is a Woman
metadata.description:
She was created from a rib cage, it is her genesis, her humble beginning. A beautiful creation whose perfect imperfection soils from the very smell of her existence to the strand of her dark hair, resolute with solid beliefs that are unfazed against high odds, her beautiful soul gazes on us beings and hypnotizes us with her gorgeousness. She is bright, alluring and assertive. Her dominance is undeniable as her body generates a desire only her hormones can sense.
Her body, the beauty and the pain she bears are unparalleled. But, her duty as a bearer of life makes her a god.
She is a Woman, she is a god, 
God is a Woman.
